            p
              | Want your RGB to shut off before bedtime but glow during the day? The OpenRGB Scheduler
              | Plugin lets you create customized schedules so that your RGB works exactly as you want
              | it to all throughout the day.
            header#pl.align-center
              a(href='https://gitlab.com/OpenRGBDevelopers/OpenRGBSchedulerPlugin')
                | GitLab
